walter satterlee january 18 , 1844 - may 28 , 1908 american figure genre painter . 
bear brooklyn , new york . 
graduate columbia university 1863 , study national academy design , edwin white , new york , leon bonnat paris . 
first exhibit national academy 1868 , elect associate academy 1879 , receive thomas b. clarke prize 1886 . 
member american water color society new york etching club , excellent teacher . 
satterlee die brooklyn 1908 . 
among favorite subject arab life figure costume colonial period . 
